<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:19:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：消息人士称奥迪新中国EV系列将不会采用标志性的四环标志</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audis-new-china-ev-series-wont-have-signature-four-ring-logo-sources-say-2024-08-02/</link><description>两位直接了解该计划的人士表示，奥迪在中国针对中国市场开发的新型电动汽车系列将不会使用其四环标志。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audis-new-china-ev-series-wont-have-signature-four-ring-logo-sources-say-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行顾问呼吁加大刺激力度，实现通胀目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</link><description>一位央行政策顾问在周五的讲话中表示，中国应加大财政刺激力度以刺激经济增长，并设定坚定的通胀目标，以防止国家陷入“低通胀陷阱”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏令全球企业增长前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</link><description>全球汉堡连锁店和汽车制造商越来越感受到世界第二大经济体中国复苏乏力的压力，并准备迎接未来的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 04:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体和网民在潘基文声称“人类不可能”完成100米游泳后团结起来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</link><description>在包括澳大利亚游泳评论员在内的批评者称潘占乐在100米自由泳中创造世界纪录“不可能”之后，中国官方媒体、运动员和网民纷纷集会支持奥运会游泳冠军潘占乐。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>长期来看，中国需要的不仅仅是“增量”消费刺激</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-needs-more-than-incremental-consumer-stimulus-longer-term-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国刺激家庭支出的努力预计将有助于经济实现政府2024年约5%的增长目标，但当局可能必须从明年开始为消费者采取更多措施，否则就接受增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 23:05:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-needs-more-than-incremental-consumer-stimulus-longer-term-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：由于增长担忧打击收益率，市场萎靡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 21:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国销量下滑，苹果寄希望于 iPhone 的人工智能升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-revenue-returns-growth-iphone-sales-top-expectations-2024-08-01/</link><description>苹果公司表示，其第三季度 iPhone 销量好于预期，并预计周四会有更多增长，因为该公司押注人工智能来吸引买家，尽管其整体中国业务令人失望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:31:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-revenue-returns-growth-iphone-sales-top-expectations-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>来自中国的原始刺蛞蝓是世界软体动物的先驱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/primordial-spiny-slug-china-was-forerunner-worlds-mollusks-2024-08-01/</link><description>地球上大约有 76,000 种软体动物，其​​形态各异，包括蛤、牡蛎、扇贝、贻贝、蜗牛、蛞蝓，甚至还有一些拥有非凡智力的软体动物，如章鱼、墨鱼和鱿鱼。但它们的祖先形态和早期进化历史一直难以破译。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/primordial-spiny-slug-china-was-forerunner-worlds-mollusks-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>EuroGroup Laminations 与中国华勤橡胶工业有限公司签署合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eurogroup-laminations-signs-partnership-with-chinas-hixih-rubber-industry-2024-08-01/</link><description>意大利电机零部件制造商 EuroGroup Laminations 周四表示，已在中国签署了一份在电动汽车领域建立战略联盟的谅解备忘录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eurogroup-laminations-signs-partnership-with-chinas-hixih-rubber-industry-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-中国范、法国选手勒布伦七局惊心动魄晋级半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-skoreas-shin-survives-thriller-brazils-calderano-makes-history-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国二号种子樊振东在第七场比赛的最后几分钟对阵日本选手张本智和，锁定了巴黎奥运会乒乓球男单半决赛的席位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 12:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-skoreas-shin-survives-thriller-brazils-calderano-makes-history-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>田径——中国杨勇夺得女子竞走金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/athletics-chinas-yang-blazes-womens-race-walk-gold-2024-08-01/</link><description>周四，中国选手杨嘉玉在巴黎奥运会女子20公里竞走比赛中夺得金牌，她在5公里大关后退出赛场，几乎没有回头看胜利，这也兑现了她对已故父亲的承诺。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:32:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/athletics-chinas-yang-blazes-womens-race-walk-gold-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>新华社称中国政策性银行原副行长被开除党籍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-vice-president-chinese-policy-bank-expelled-communist-party-xinhua-says-2024-08-01/</link><description>据新华社周四报道，国家开发银行原副行长李继平因涉嫌严重违纪违法，被开除党籍。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-vice-president-chinese-policy-bank-expelled-communist-party-xinhua-says-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官：中国对关税问题持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-china-is-open-discussion-tariffs-2024-08-01/</link><description>大众汽车首席执行官表示，中国和欧洲应该建立关税制度，奖励那些投资国内汽车生产的人，并补充说，他最近在北京会见的中国部长们愿意进行讨论，旨在寻求公平的解决方案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-china-is-open-discussion-tariffs-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>我国拟加强智能网联汽车OTA升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-plans-strengthen-intelligent-connected-vehicles-ota-upgrade-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国工信部周四发布了智能网联汽车召回和无线软件升级规则草案，旨在加强对OTA升级的监管，OTA升级在中国法规下的电动汽车产品召回中已成为常见现象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-plans-strengthen-intelligent-connected-vehicles-ota-upgrade-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>射击-男子50米步枪三项赛中国选手刘勇夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-liu-wins-mens-50-metre-rifle-three-position-gold-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国选手刘玉坤周四在巴黎奥运会男子 50 米步枪三项比赛中获得金牌，随后自信地宣称自己可能是这项运动的“天才”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 08:32:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-liu-wins-mens-50-metre-rifle-three-position-gold-2024-08-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>